posting_body: ['Guarantors Welcome', 'Gorgeous 2 Bed 1 Bath available in Ocean Hill, walking distance from the Rockaway Ave C and Bushwick Ave L train lines.', 'The surrounding area is home to many corner cafes, coffee shops, cool bars, great restaurants, and organic grocery stores!', 'Key features:', '- Beautiful kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances', '- 2 Queen Size Bedrooms w/ big closets and big windows with lots of Natural Lights', '- Spacious living room', '- Exposed Brick', '- 1 Bathroom w/ Deep Soaking Tub', '- Central AC / HEAT', '- Virtual Doorman', '- Laundry in Building', '- Pets Welcome', 'Move in is first month’s rent ($2650), security deposit ($2650) and broker’s fee ($2650).', 'Contact me today before it’s gone!', 'Mike B. 831-585-0112']
